"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![Docs | Website | Twitter | Discord | Telegram](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*C8pYEQEAxsyTis0vif5W6w.png)\\n\\nHipo Decentralized Bond Protocol is a digital assets institution offering instant crypto loans, daily earning on assets and earning on liquidity providing.\\n\\n## Borrow\\n\\nAs collateral, various LPs Tokens from Quickswap are accepted, such as ETH/USDC, ETH/DAI and USDT/ETH. Having pledged assets, you get correlated currency as loan by issuing bonds. You can set term for bonds as 5 days, 10 days, 15 days, 30 days, 45 days and 60 days. Interest is paid while issuing bonds. The maximum borrowing amount is related to the value of collateral. At expiration date, you redeem bonds with full face value. You can also redeem bonds before maturity.\\n\\n## Earn Fixed Income\\n\\nWhile buying crypto and holding it until the price goes up is a great option for turning a profit, it requires lots of time and a bit of luck. With Hipo, you can put your idle assets to work straight away and have a predictable source of passive income without the risk. Create your Hipo account and go from zero to earning in less than a minute. All you have to do is: choose the currency and amount of your portfolio, set the term, purchase bonds and start earning. After maturity, you can withdraw your principle and claim the rewards. The income you get is fixed. If you want to withdraw before maturity, you can reset the term and trade the bonds in trading market.\",\"timestamp\":1639477806,\"title\":\"Borrow and Earn on Hipo \"},\"digest\":\"6zOLu6vvWj-D88eT_ORBI9ouFzD9vgCNctF-9mxaixk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xcb07030a5d4dDAd40B552bB512D97d523d6F6668\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cTNnb3mlkyc-4WWiaF36hgivm08OAJWDp-2UQz1JXzY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"hR0DQjyRqCsiLMmdljdgUJyO_FZh6RJp4AdsO2_7tfs\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"mCzfcWABNJKxUPSA_eh6VrKwNKUVrM5Tzvpo